# Cursed items in use
MENUCOLOR=" cursed .* \(weapon in .*\)"=orange&underline
MENUCOLOR=" cursed .* \(wielded.*\)"=orange&underline
MENUCOLOR=" cursed .* \(alternate weapon\)"=orange&underline
MENUCOLOR=" cursed .* \(in quiver\)"=orange&underline
